{"tid":890361,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【銀主腳軟】滙豐劈價280萬沽港景峯銀主盤","createTime":"2018-11-05T09:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T15:20:09.000Z","uid":169895,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"93e6bde44fa841266431229883758439c52568cb","tid":890361,"uid":169895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181105/58877265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181105%2F58877265&d=wM3bPP5psT4qZB%2BIA%2FDayr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=26935c02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181105%2F58877265&h=93e878f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181105/58877265</a><br />\n<br />\n樓市淡靜，連龍頭滙豐銀行也減價沽售銀主盤。<br />\n九龍站豪宅近期交投死寂，上月僅擎天半島一宗「自讓盤」成交，面對交投如此淡靜，銀主盤也要劈價求售。消息指港景峯3座低層B室，實用面積750方呎，三房間隔，銀主為滙豐銀行，去年12月以1,880萬元市價放盤，上月減至1,720萬元低於市價仍無人問津，銀主腳軟，剛累減280萬至1,600萬元終能沽貨，呎價僅21,333元，創屋苑今年新低價。<br />\n本報於滙豐銀行網站為該銀主盤估值，滙豐估值仍達1,856萬元，今次滙豐沽貨比自己估值還要低出14%。同座中高層B室，實用面積780方呎，今年4月以2,068萬元沽出，呎26,513元。<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，該銀主盤賣方於2012年以1,130萬元買入單位，曾有多次加按紀錄，至2014年由滙豐銀行承造一按，最終疑斷供物業落入銀主手中。"},{"pid":"5e87f25e935f589728a807da9794b5f404a1c2a8","tid":890361,"uid":10152,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:18:26.000Z","msg":"銀主盤唔計"},{"pid":"8d8af6931180db380578812b2be7e2e4dcd6b302","tid":890361,"uid":9069,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"280萬捱義氣幫你買"},{"pid":"f728d3eb18de97b00d63876dfb0254cb27218a87","tid":890361,"uid":42921,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T09:25:08.000Z","msg":"銀行都係廢淡，唔識strong hold"},{"pid":"88633eba2c4c2691cd56c3479d4d60890fbf5e88","tid":890361,"uid":5686,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201